 without understanding the science of self-realization.” This human form of life is a most valuable asset for the living entity, who can utilize it for solving the problems of life; therefore, one who does not utilize this opportunity properly is a miser. On the other hand, there is the \u003cem\u003ebrāhmaṇa,\u003c/em\u003e or he who is intelligent enough to utilize this body to solve all the problems of life. \u003cem\u003eYa etad akṣaraṁ gārgi viditvāsmāl lokāt praiti sa brāhmaṇaḥ.\u003c/em\u003e\"},{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"paragraph\",\"id\":489,\"bb\":446,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/7/b446/\",\"body_value\":\"$33\"}]}],\"short_title\":\"Bg. 2.7\",\"medium_title\":\"Bhagavad-gītā As It Is 2.7\"},{\"id\":490,\"meta\":{\"type\":\"books.Verse\",\"slug\":\"8\",\"show_in_menus\":false,\"seo_title\":\"\",\"search_description\":\"\",\"first_published_at\":null,\"alias_of\":null,\"locale\":\"en\"},\"title\":\"TEXT 8\",\"advanced_view_url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/advanced-view/#bb447\",\"language_menu\":[{\"display_name\":\"አማርኛ (Ethiopian)\",\"language_code\":\"am\",\"enabled\":false,\"url_path\":\"/am/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Български (Bulgarian)\",\"language_code\":\"bg\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/bg/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Čeština (Czech)\",\"language_code\":\"cs\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/cs/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Dansk (Danish)\",\"language_code\":\"da\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/da/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Deutsch (German)\",\"language_code\":\"de\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/de/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"English\",\"language_code\":\"en\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Español (Spanish)\",\"language_code\":\"es\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/es/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Eesti keel (Estonian)\",\"language_code\":\"et\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/et/library/bg/2/8/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Suomen 