\",\"body_final\":\"अविनाशि तु तद्विद्धि येन सर्वमिदं ततम् ।\u003cbr/\u003eविनाशमव्ययस्यास्य न कश्चित्कर्तुमर्हति ॥ १७ ॥\"}]},{\"section\":\"verse_text\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.verse-text\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"content.Record\",\"title\":\"verse_text\",\"id\":561,\"bb\":510,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/17/b510/\",\"body_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eavināśi tu tad viddhi\u003cbr /\u003eyena sarvam idaṁ tatam\u003cbr /\u003evināśam avyayasyāsya\u003cbr /\u003ena kaścit kartum arhati\u003c/em\u003e\"}]},{\"section\":\"synonyms\",\"section_title\":\"Books.Verse.synonyms\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"books.Synonyms\",\"title\":\"synonyms\",\"id\":562,\"bb\":511,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/17/b511/\",\"shadow_value\":\"\u003cem\u003eavināśi\u003c/em\u003e – imperishable; \u003cem\u003etu\u003c/em\u003e – but; \u003cem\u003etat\u003c/em\u003e – that; \u003cem\u003eviddhi\u003c/em\u003e – know it; \u003cem\u003eyena\u003c/em\u003e – by whom; \u003cem\u003esarvam\u003c/em\u003e – all of the body; \u003cem\u003eidam\u003c/em\u003e – this; \u003cem\u003etatam\u003c/em\u003e – pervaded; \u003cem\u003evināśam\u003c/em\u003e – destruction; \u003cem\u003eavyayasya\u003c/em\u003e – of the imperishable; \u003cem\u003easya\u003c/em\u003e – of it; \u003cem\u003ena kaścit\u003c/em\u003e – no one; \u003cem\u003ekartum\u003c/em\u003e – to do; \u003cem\u003earhati\u003c/em\u003e – is able.\",\"word_for_word_value\":[{\"word\":\"avināśi\",\"translation\":\"imperishable\"},{\"word\":\"tu\",\"translation\":\"but\"},{\"word\":\"tat\",\"translation\":\"that\"},{\"word\":\"viddhi\",\"translation\":\"know it\"},{\"word\":\"yena\",\"translation\":\"by whom\"},{\"word\":\"sarvam\",\"translation\":\"all of the body\"},{\"word\":\"idam\",\"translation\":\"this\"},{\"word\":\"tatam\",\"translation\":\"pervaded\"},{\"word\":\"vināśam\",\"translation\":\"destruction\"},{\"word\":\"avyayasya\",\"translation\":\"of the imperishable\"},{\"word\":\"asya\",\"translation\":\"of it\"},{\"word\":