per duty, he would not be able to stop the death of his relatives, and he would be degraded due to his selection of the wrong path of action.\"}]}],\"short_title\":\"Bg. 2.27\",\"medium_title\":\"Bhagavad-gītā As It Is 2.27\"},{\"id\":651,\"meta\":{\"type\":\"books.Verse\",\"slug\":\"28\",\"show_in_menus\":false,\"seo_title\":\"\",\"search_description\":\"\",\"first_published_at\":null,\"alias_of\":null,\"locale\":\"en\"},\"title\":\"TEXT 28\",\"advanced_view_url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/advanced-view/#bb590\",\"language_menu\":[{\"display_name\":\"አማርኛ (Ethiopian)\",\"language_code\":\"am\",\"enabled\":false,\"url_path\":\"/am/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Български (Bulgarian)\",\"language_code\":\"bg\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/bg/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Čeština (Czech)\",\"language_code\":\"cs\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/cs/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Dansk (Danish)\",\"language_code\":\"da\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/da/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Deutsch (German)\",\"language_code\":\"de\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/de/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"English\",\"language_code\":\"en\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/en/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Español (Spanish)\",\"language_code\":\"es\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/es/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Eesti keel (Estonian)\",\"language_code\":\"et\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/et/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Suomen kieli (Finnish)\",\"language_code\":\"fi\",\"enabled\":false,\"url_path\":\"/fi/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Français (French)\",\"language_code\":\"fr\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/fr/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Hrvatski (Croatian)\",\"language_code\":\"hr\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/hr/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"Magyar (Hungarian)\",\"language_code\":\"hu\",\"enabled\":true,\"url_path\":\"/hu/library/bg/2/28/\"},{\"display_name\":\"한국어 (Korean)\",\"langua