ed man, he was consequently lamenting for something which was unworthy of lamentation. The body is born and is destined to be vanquished today or tomorrow; therefore the body is not as important as the soul. One who knows this is actually learned, and for him there is no cause for lamentation, regardless of the condition of the material body.90:[\"$\",\"div\",\"515-purport,515-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,":mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-520\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:10:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$1c6\"}}]}]]]}]\n91:[\"$\",\"div\",\"521-devanagari,521-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-522\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:11:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"न त्वेवाहं जातु नासं न त्वं नेमे जनाधिपाः ।\u003cbr/\u003eन चैव नभविष्यामः सर्वे वयमतः परम् ॥ १२ ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\n92:[\"$\",\"div\",\"521-verse_text,521-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"av-verse_text\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Verse text\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-523\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:11:child_items:1:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leadin