 instantly help one onto the platform of transcendental consciousness. The highly developed soul always remains satisfied in himself by realizing himself as the eternal servitor of the Supreme Lord. Such a transcendentally situated person has no sense desires resulting from petty materialism; rather, he remains always happy in his natural position of eternally serving the Supreme Lord.167:[\"$\",\"div\",\"851-purport,851-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"clas"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"sName\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-856\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:53:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$1de\"}}]}]]]}]\n168:[\"$\",\"div\",\"857-devanagari,857-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-858\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:54:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"दुःखेष्वनुद्विग्न‍मनाः सुखेषु विगतस्पृहः ।\u003cbr/\u003eवीतरागभयक्रोधः स्थिधीर्मुनिरुच्यते ॥ ५६ ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\n169:[\"$\",\"div\",\"857-verse_text,857-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"av-verse_text\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Verse text\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-859\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:54:child_items:1:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",