 (\u003cem\u003eīśāvāsyam idaṁ sarvam\u003c/em\u003e), and therefore he does not falsely claim proprietorship over anything. This transcendental knowledge is based on self-realizat"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"ion – namely, knowing perfectly well that every living entity is an eternal part and parcel of Kṛṣṇa in spiritual identity, and that the eternal position of the living entity is therefore never on the level of Kṛṣṇa or greater than Him. This understanding of Kṛṣṇa consciousness is the basic principle of real peace.1b6:[\"$\",\"div\",\"957-purport,957-purport\",{\"className\":\"av-purport\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4\",\"children\":\"Purport\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-962\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:69:child_items:4:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-base s-justify\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$1e5\"}}]}]]]}]\n1b7:[\"$\",\"div\",\"963-devanagari,963-devanagari\",{\"className\":\"av-devanagari\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Devanagari\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-964\",{\"child\":\"$2b:props:children:0:props:children:props:page:child_items:0:children:70:child_items:0:children:0\",\"hasId\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"em:mb-4 em:leading-8 em:text-lg text-center\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"एषा ब्राह्मी स्थितिःपार्थ नैनां प्राप्य विमुह्यति ।\u003cbr/\u003eस्थित्वास्यामन्तकालेऽपि ब्रह्मनिर्वाणमृच्छति ॥ ७२ ॥\"}}]}]]]}]\n1b8:[\"$\",\"div\",\"963-verse_text,963-verse_text\",{\"className\":\"av-verse_text\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-center em:leading-5 em:text-xl font-bold em:mb-4 hidden\",\"children\":\"Verse text\"}],[[\"$\",\"$L59\",\"child-965\",{\"child\":\"$2b:prop